"""
max25d — MainAX25-Stack daemon (Linux only).

Owns config, plugin hardware lifecycle, and M25/1 IPC for max25-terminal clients.
Supports multiple concurrent heterogeneous devices (TNC, BayCom, CRDOP) via backends.
"""
